{"tid":280490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人]KFC\"臭雞\"絲打","createTime":"2017-06-12T06:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T09:08:50.000Z","uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14bed142302d075cc7904c8161119102ddf785ae","tid":280490,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"剛剛係KFC，<br />\n有兩位女生，吹水講周遊列國，講晒粗口咁<br />\n本來講粗口係要扣少少分，<br />\n點知某位突然勁大聲鬧男友既前女友，<br />\n成間KFC都聽到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">: 屌佢老母，姣人條仔，直情係正一臭...um...ar...<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一次係現實世界見到絲打發威，果句含蓄而帶有嬌羞既臭雞說，真係覇氣盡露。<br />\n<br />\n希望絲打唔好咁介意自己brand 3既學歷喇，識講&quot;臭雞&quot;依個terms既女人已經完勝一堆大學妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e80375b40076b0fd2b0641caac40ad052eabef4","tid":280490,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"阿豬阿狗都識講啦on9"},{"pid":"be853d39c22abf46588955e013ac6824b39e6986","tid":280490,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"你又知人band 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c3a0f9dff32cffcaa80c2656b72c6ea66eaf9c","tid":280490,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿豬阿狗都識講啦on9</blockquote><br />\n我搵欣宜講俾你聽<br />\n到時你咪又係話人粗魯<br />\n講到尾都係個樣"},{"pid":"4b98efb80ba4a211e27d455f6ee381d4276aef3a","tid":280490,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"08b5193ab91893ec45262a179952eeef37c83e10","tid":280490,"uid":93078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"作得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb608df588df7d17d30fd9d8d963b7f93f5b3c4f","tid":280490,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"白汁有d雞皇 就26蚊"},{"pid":"9fe5308f503bd12825d6e87d874d237411598fbc","tid":280490,"uid":55823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"你又知係絲打"},{"pid":"284cfc04cf2f6e837237dd8515a55a8e4be4f78e","tid":280490,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係真嫁，連我個名都係真嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1959b363fba181c01a9a82d2ce4b6b9a81ded99c","tid":280490,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又知係絲打</blockquote><br />\n除左一眾安答，<br />\n普通既常人，會係街上面大大聲叫人臭雞嗎?"},{"pid":"c0f73d4c771774e42529a41c9188f8df417ae779","tid":280490,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}